WEBVTT

00:00:58.328 --> 00:01:00.731
Mgonjwa huyo alikuwa serikali yangu.

00:01:02.126 --> 00:01:03.276
(Vicheko)

00:01:04.102 --> 00:01:07.704
Tazama, wengi wetu tunakubaliana kwamba serikali zetu leo zina afya mbovu.

00:01:08.876 --> 00:01:10.959
(Vicheko)

00:01:10.983 --> 00:01:15.617
(Makofi)

00:01:16.814 --> 00:01:18.556
Na Kenya haina upekee.

00:01:18.975 --> 00:01:21.478
Niliporudi Kenya mwaka 2014,

00:01:21.502 --> 00:01:24.206
asilimia 17 ya vijana hawakuwa na ajira.

00:01:24.785 --> 00:01:27.133
Na Nairobi, kitovu kuu cha biashara ,

00:01:27.157 --> 00:01:31.232
ilikuwa ya 177 kwa ubora wa maisha duniani.